data.description: Brand new Santa Rosa town home. This home has many custom touches like 12 X 24 plank tile from the front door to the lanai, stainless steel appliances, and granite in the kitchen, along with the upgraded diamond shaped tile back splash. The owner's suite is on the main level and features a large shower, dual sink raised vanity in Espresso with Crema Pearl granite counter tops. The loft area on the second floor makes a great second family room, game room or office area. The other two secondary bedrooms are adjacent to the loft, with a full bath with dual sink raised vanity.This open floor plan is perfect for entertaining or just hanging out with the family. The designer kitchen has 42" upper cabinets in Espresso with Crema Pearl granite counter tops, stainless steel appliances,island with breakfast bar. The island in the kitchen is a perfect spot to eat, do food prep or gather with friends. Spacious screened lanai out back is perfect to spend warm summer evenings.
